**  TBL1/TBL2 (UPDATE /NAME)
0-CANCEL
1-CHANGE
2-ADD
**  ERR
E-01 UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS WRONG
E-02 IN CASE OF ADD INPUT INTRAL COMPANY PART NO
E-03 IN CASE OF ADD INPUT PUBLICATION INSTRUCTION
E-04 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT IS IN M/F
E-05 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT ISN'T IN M/F
E-06 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-07 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT IS NOT IN M/F
E-08 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-09 INPUT USER CODE
E-10 USER CODE IS WRONG
E-11 THERE IS NOT USER CODE IN DETAILS M/F
E-12 INPUT FACTORY
E-13 INPUT RECEIVING
E-14 INPUT CHANGE  PROGRAM
E-15 CHANGE PROGRAM IS WRONG
E-16 CHANGE INSTRUCTION IS WRONG
E-17 INPUT STOCK NUMBER
E-18 INPUT NUMBER OF BOXES
E-19 INPUT WEIGHT
E-20 PROD ORDER BOOK RECEIPT DAY IS WRONG
E-21 INPUT PERSON IN CHARGE
E-22 STOCK ANSWER DAY IS WRONG
E-23 CHANGE ENFORCEMENT DAY IS WRONG
